Question: Are there either any black couches or mirrors?

Reference Answer: no

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n295771.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='couches')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='mirrors')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the couches?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the mirrors?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'black' or {ANSWER1} == 'black' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
